These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, begonia
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, cricket
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the owner of the pony is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Flower         | dahlia | balloon-flower   | begonia   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Pet   | pony  | hedgehog    | horse      |
| Sport     | water-polo     | rowing      | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
City: nizza, prague, boston
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, aristoff, vegafina
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, sunflower
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person traveling to prague is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is between the fan of gospel and the person traveling to boston##2
6. the person traveling to boston is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| City          | prague  | nizza     | boston     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Cigar   | vegafina  | aristoff | montecristo |
| Flower           | sunflower | marigold     | poppy       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, almond-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, cain, prince
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
City: edinburgh, nizza, venice
1. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the prince-smoker and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage          | water  | almond-milk     | fanta     |
| Cigar           | prince | blend  | cain   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| City           | venice     | edinburgh | nizza |

