.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, horror, mystery
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, disco, metal
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, roller, quad-bike
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the fan of metal##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is between the fan of disco and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person watching horror movies is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre    | musical       | mystery  | horror   |
| Music-Genre     | disco    | metal  | country |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter     | roller      |

