The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, baseball, weightlifting
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, baccarat, vegafina
3 different pets are kept: bird, dog, hamster
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the vegafina-smoker and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the owner of the dog##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage          | fanta    | 7up     | tea      |
| Sport         | swimming | baseball | weightlifting |
| Cigar   | vegafina  | baccarat       | montecristo       |
| Pet           | dog     | bird       | hamster     |

