.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, november, may
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, manager, project-manager
City: new-york, nizza, paris
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the project-manager##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is the software-developer##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is between the person who's birthday is in november and the owner of the horse##2
4. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Birthday          | november | september | may    |
| Job         | manager | project-manager      | software-developer |
| City   | new-york   | nizza     | paris        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

