.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, radish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, ambient, funk
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, soy-milk
City: marseilles, hamburg, hannover
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the fan of ambient is between the person eating radish and the person traveling to marseilles##2
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of funk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Music-Genre         | gospel | ambient | funk |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | soy-milk | coffee   |
| City     | hannover         | hamburg  | marseilles       |

