3 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, frog
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, japanese, chinese
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
1. the chinese is on the far left##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the indonesian is between the owner of the chinchilla and the victorian house##2
5. the ranch-style house is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| House      | gothic-revival       | ranch-style      | victorian      |
| Pet         | chinchilla    | frog | hamster      |
| Nationality           | chinese | indonesian     | japanese |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | rock          | folk       |

