.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, billiard
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, police-officer, scientist
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, nigerian, russian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, april, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is between the nigerian and the russian##2
2. the scientist is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
4. the police-officer is on the far left##1
5. the indian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Game      | scrabble      | snooker | billiard     |
| Job          | police-officer   | dressmaker      | scientist     |
| Nationality   | russian  | indian      | nigerian |
| Birthday     | january | march        | april     |

