.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, drawing, traveling
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, grapefruit, strawberry
3 different games are played: chess, billiard, snooker
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, argentine
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating pineapple and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person playing snooker is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person playing billiard is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
6. the canadian is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | drawing       | traveling       | chess    |
| Food         | strawberry | grapefruit | pineapple |
| Game       | billiard      | snooker         | chess |
| Nationality   | canadian        | argentine            | chinese  |

