.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, disaster, martial-arts
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, writing
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, freelancer, videographer
3 different games are played: domino, scrabble, snooker
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the freelancer##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
4. the person playing scrabble is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the videographer is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Movie-Genre      | martial-arts     | disaster | epic      |
| Hobby         | reading  | writing       | board-games |
| Job   | videographer   | freelancer         | dancer     |
| Game   | domino | scrabble    | snooker     |

