.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, monopoly
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, tulip
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, musical, sports
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, blood-red, black
1. the person playing canasta is the person who growstulip##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes black##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing canasta is between the person who growsrose and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Game      | backgammon | canasta      | monopoly            |
| Flower           | iris | tulip | rose |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| Color   | blood-red  | grey    | black        |

