3. the police-officer is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the person playing billiard is the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| City      | colone    | miami          | nizza |
