The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, baseball, tennis
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, skydiving, reading
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, software-developer, entrepreneur
1. the person who's sport is baseball is between the entrepreneur and the person who's sport is sailing##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of disco##1
5. the videographer is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| Sport   | tennis    | baseball | sailing |
| Hobby           | singing        | reading   | skydiving  |
| Job     | entrepreneur      | software-developer   | videographer |

