The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, climbing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, zombie, animation
1. the person watching zombie movies is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the fan of disco is between the polish and the person who's sport is badminton##2
4. the fan of reggae is the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching musical movies is between the chinese and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Nationality      | polish | japanese     | chinese        |
| Sport         | baseball   | climbing | badminton |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Movie-Genre           | animation           | musical    | zombie       |

