.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, rock, country
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, drawing
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, chef, social-worker
1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the writer##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is the writer##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of country##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre        | rock      | r&b | country |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Hobby       | chess | drawing   | puzzles   |
| Job   | writer          | chef     | social-worker       |

 